{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述郭大路、王动、燕七、林太平四人在严冬中穷困潦倒，数冰柱度日。林太平当掉自己的厚衣服换来四个馒头与大家分享，体现了患难中的真挚友谊。郭大路翻跟斗时意外掉出一条金链子，暴露了他一直隐藏的秘密——他曾深爱的未婚妻朱珠在婚前与马夫私奔，这条金链子是她的订情之物。朋友们没有追问，默默给予理解。郭大路最终向朋友们坦白了这段痛苦往事，王动等人开导他从好的方面看待这件事，帮助他释怀。当铺老板活剥皮突然来访，提出给五百两银子让四人陪他去县城走一趟，四人虽然穷困但拒绝了这笔来路不明的钱，坚守尊严和原则。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "平忽然问",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们猜这里一共有多少根冰柱子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "六十三根。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "二十六根长，三十七根短。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "住笑了，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你们也数过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已数过四十遍。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只数过三遍，因为我舍不得多数。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "舍不得？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我要留着慢慢地数。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "眨眨眼，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要不要我来试试。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你根本不必试。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这桌上什么也没有呀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "面子！而且不是我一个人的面子，是我们大家的面子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "气，苦笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，这桌子我的确抬不起来。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪种人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要脸的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "了口气，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那种人通常都是吃得很饱的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "猪通常也都吃得很饱的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为人不是猪，只有猪才会认为肚子比面子重要。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以有人宁可饿死，也不愿做丢人的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我们并没有饿死，是不是？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们虽然已有好几天都没有吃饱，但总算已捱到现在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要我们肯捱下去，总有一天能捱到转机的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路展颜笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，冬天既已来了，春天还会远吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "于忍不住",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们能捱得过去吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "大路抢着",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "纸包，笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们猜，我带了什么东西回来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "眨眨眼，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道是馒头？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "林太平笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "答对了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "大路欢呼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "林太平万岁！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "林太平，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些馒头当然不是变出来的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "笑了笑，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许是天上掉下来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "摇摇头，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不吃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "了口气，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我不忍吃你的衣服。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，你就该吃完了再回来，也免得我们……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自私？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "林太平笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说的话不老实，这只不过是个冷馒头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "了口气，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜我这件衣服太破。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "破衣服并不丢人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "郭大路叹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜那活剥皮绝不会这么想，否则……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "七笑笑，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "否则你早就脱下来去换酒了，对不对？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "大路苦笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "答对了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "用不着去试，你的衣服比我还破。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "寒夜客来茶当酒，茶既然可以当酒，水为什么不能？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "大路失笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到你倒很风雅。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "燕七笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你干什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "摇摇头，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我也有经验，动得快，饿得也快。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "郭大路笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想得太多了，只要现在不冷，又何必……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "抬起头，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么不去睡？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还在等。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等着听你说……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能说……我怎么能说？……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎么还有脸留在这里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友们，再见吧，总有一天，你们会了解我的。到那一天，我们还是朋友，可是现在……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "了几声，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们不是已睡了吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们睡不着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里就比被窝里好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里有哪点好？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只有一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里有朋友，被窝里没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "他垂下头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里也没有朋友，我已不配做你们的朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也没有说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们到这里来，只想说一句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "了拳头。",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论发生了什么事，你都是我们的朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的马夫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么教训？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "燕七忽然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说我错了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么原因？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那只因她天生是个坏女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "王动忽然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种想法也不对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不对？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本来难道不是这样子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你至少应该往别的地方想想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我应该怎么想？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想想好的那一面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "大路苦笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想不出。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你有没有亲眼看到她和那个马夫做出什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你又怎么能断定她是和那马夫私奔的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但她的确是和那马夫在同一天突然失踪的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那也许只不过是巧合。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天下哪有这么巧的事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有。不但有，而且常常有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么他们为什么要突然走了呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "太平忽然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许她一直都很想向你解释，却一直没有机会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "更痛苦的是，别人根本就不给他机会解释。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最痛苦的是，有些事根本就不能对别人解释的，譬如说……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，现在你已想通了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "了，大声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说我是这种人，我打扁他的鼻子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们虽然分别了，说不定反而能活得更快乐些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "每个人都有自己的命运，你既不能勉强，也不必勉强。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 702
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你根本没有什么事好痛苦的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 704
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "娘舅来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "娘舅",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 718,
      "line_end": 718
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "活剥皮",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 718,
      "line_end": 718
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拜访",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 730
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "假如他肯便宜卖呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 746,
      "line_end": 746
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我买来干什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 748,
      "line_end": 748
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可以再转让给别人，也可以自己住进来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有毛病的人，谁肯住进这种地方来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 752,
      "line_end": 752
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "王动笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们哪天不缺钱用？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 758,
      "line_end": 758
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那你们想不想平白赚五百两银子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 760,
      "line_end": 760
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "眨眨眼，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说的是五百两？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 770,
      "line_end": 770
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "整整五百两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 772,
      "line_end": 772
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "他几眼，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是不是喝酒了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 774,
      "line_end": 774
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "了口气，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这银子要怎么样才能赚得到呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 780
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走一趟？怎么走法？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 786,
      "line_end": 786
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然是用两条腿走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 788,
      "line_end": 788
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "了两步，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就这么样走？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 790,
      "line_end": 790
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 792,
      "line_end": 792
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "然后呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 794,
      "line_end": 794
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "然后你们就可以带着五百两银子走回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 796,
      "line_end": 796
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有别的事了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 798,
      "line_end": 798
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 800,
      "line_end": 800
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 806,
      "line_end": 806
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有很多事你们都没有听说过，但却并不是假的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 808,
      "line_end": 808
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你赔本也不是假的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 810,
      "line_end": 810
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "忍不住问",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是赔本的生意，你为什么还要做呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 818,
      "line_end": 818
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮叹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那也是没法子，唉，谁叫我当初选了这一行呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 820,
      "line_end": 820
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以那五百两银子你还是留着自己慢慢用吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 822,
      "line_end": 822
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "剥皮抢着",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那不同，那是我自己愿意让你们赚的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 824,
      "line_end": 824
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么用意？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 834,
      "line_end": 834
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 840,
      "line_end": 840
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "剥皮愕然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "五百两银子你不想要？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 842,
      "line_end": 842
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 844,
      "line_end": 844
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 846,
      "line_end": 846
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有原因。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 848,
      "line_end": 848
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "，忽又笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你一个人不去也没关系，我还是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 850,
      "line_end": 850
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "燕七忽然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不是一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 852,
      "line_end": 852
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也不去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 854,
      "line_end": 854
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也不去，而且也没有原因，不去就是不去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 856,
      "line_end": 856
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "了，大声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的银子难道不好？你们难道没拿过？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 862,
      "line_end": 862
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "王动淡淡",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们若要你的银子，自然会拿东西去当的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 864,
      "line_end": 864
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 870,
      "line_end": 870
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "气，忽然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么不问？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 900,
      "line_end": 900
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "问什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 902,
      "line_end": 902
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你没有看到这里少了一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 904,
      "line_end": 904
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "点点头，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好像是少了一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 906,
      "line_end": 906
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
